title: Nissin Oillio Meal Green Tea With Dietary Fiber 60 Packets
description: "Green tea with dietary fiber 6g * 60 packets for meals" is a powdered green tea with dietary fiber that can be easily dissolved in hot or cold water. A water-soluble dietary fiber, a type of dietary fiber made from starch, the indigestible dextrin slows down the rate at which sugars in the diet are absorbed from the small intestine, and moderates the rapid rise in blood sugar levels after eating.   Ideal for those who are worried about blood sugar levels. Contains an aluminum stick that is convenient for carrying. We recommend both daily meals. Approved by the Ministry of Health, Labor and Welfare, food for specified health use.
